data.description: This gorgeous property in Laurel Glen combines elegance, functionality, and a prime location. You'll find yourself just moments away from top-rated schools, parks, shopping, and dining. Every detail of this home has been carefully crafted to create a space that you'll be proud to call your own. This house boasts high vaulted ceilings, letting in plenty of natural light that creates a bright and open space. When you step into the backyard you are greeted by an oversized covered patio and a sparkling pool. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home. Schedule your showing today and experience the beauty that Laurel Glen has to offer. Your dream home awaits!
